entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Yon moman nan feblès. Youn. Anplis, Marlon ak mwen te sou yon repo?" t="One moment of weakness. One. Besides, Marlon and I were on a break." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Yon moman, ou te pran yon repo pou, preske, de jou?" t="Hang on, you guys took a break for, like, two days." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Kisa? Yon repo se yon repo?" t="So? A break's a break." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Hm. Li te?" t="Hm. Was he?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ugh, ou memn tou? Non, mwen pa konnen. Li pa pi bon o pi mal. Jis diferan?" t="Ugh, you too? No, I dunno. He wasn't better or worse. Just different." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Si sa kontinye, mwen pral deplase. Mwen pa ka pran sa ankò?" t="If this goes on, I'm gonna move out. I can't take this anymore." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ba li yon chans. Ou pa wè, li ba ou youn?" t="Give him a chance. After all, he is giving you one." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="'Jan mwen wè li, li pa te kopye, men li pa vle kite li ale" t="So as I see it, it wasn't cheating. But he just won't let it go?" b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="creo" o="Li vin gen depresyon…anmède mwen sou li. O Li kòmanse mande si lòt nèg la te pi bon. Tankou li nan yon konpetisyon?" t="He gets depressed or... bugs me about it. Or he starts askin' if the other guy was better. Like it's a contest or somethin'." b="" a=""/>
